{"type": "article", "id": 9448, "title": "“Hub+” 接口器", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-12T07:11:12Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 27, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235324WD37p8aSB9cKg4Lu.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t12 寸的 Apple MacBook 让很多人望而却步的一个原因是 USB-C 接口带来的通用性差，来自家加州的团队 Nonda 推出了一款叫做 “Hub+” 的接口器，提供两个 USB-C 接口、一个 SDXC 读卡器、三个 USB-A 接口和一个支持 4K 显示的视频输出接口。同时，它内置了一个容量 400mAh 的电池，可为手机提供 2 个小时电源。目前产品正在 Kickstarter 众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nonda/get-your-macbook-ports-back\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以支持他们</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235321GNW8HwSjJZgR54uO.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.59814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235321CXRvNyh8nMkDfsb1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.76944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235322RPoNn6Tkzg13CxmQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.2537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235322oIBA5HlFwNETQjYh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.31857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235322SfpnqFTNHaOsWYmr.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235323Ti2qF1bkfZBhdvKc.gif\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66714286\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}